'''2015年东南亚霾害'''是一場影響[[東南亞|東南亞]]多個國家的[[空氣污染|空氣污染]]危機，受災地區包括[[汶萊|汶萊]]、[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]（印尼；特別是[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]和[[加里曼丹|加里曼丹]]島）、 [[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[泰國|泰國]]南部、[[越南|越南]]南部和[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]，甚至[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]、[[馬里亞納群島|馬里亞納群島]]和[[關島|關島]]<ref>{{cite web|title=South-East Asian haze strikes the Pacific as fires exceed greenhouse gas output of the US|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-10-21/se-asian-fires-producing-more-greenhouse-gas-than-us-report-says/6874598|accessdate=21 October 2015|publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Company|Australian Broadcasting Company]]|archive-date=2015-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028184618/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-10-21/se-asian-fires-producing-more-greenhouse-gas-than-us-report-says/6874598|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霾害最遲在6月底出現<ref name=June15>{{cite web|title=Haze envelopes parts of Riau province in Indonesia|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-envelopes-parts-of-riau-province-in-indonesia|work=The Straits Times|accessdate=2015-10-11|date=2015-06-30|archive-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116233408/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-envelopes-parts-of-riau-province-in-indonesia|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並從9月開始蔓延到其他國家，最終成為國際問題。[[東南亞霾害|霾害]]是當地的一個長期問題，當地每逢旱季便會遭遇強弱不一的霾害<ref>{{cite web|title = Why is South-East Asia's annual haze so hard to deal with?|url = http://www.economist.com/blogs/economist-explains/2013/07/economist-explains-3|work = The Economist|date = 2013-07-07|accessdate = 2015-10-02|archive-date = 2015-09-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150926014621/http://www.economist.com/blogs/economist-explains/2013/07/economist-explains-3|dead-url = no}}</ref>。霧霾由主要在印尼蘇門答臘和加里曼丹進行的非法[[刀耕火種|刀耕火種]]活動（當地俗稱燒芭）引發的[[山火|山火]]引起，而且會在旱季期間迅速擴散<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/business-23026219|title=South East Asia haze: What is slash-and-burn?|publisher=BBC|date=2013-06-24|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010044710/http://www.bbc.com/news/business-23026219|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34242311 |title= Haze chokes Indonesia, Malaysia and Singapore |publisher= BBC |date= 2015-09-15 |accessdate= 2015-09-25 |archive-date= 2015-09-28 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150928103734/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34242311 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/riau-declares-emergency-as-haze-worsens |title = Image of Asia: Wildfires in Indonesia Spread Haze |publisher = The Associated Press |work = The Straits Times |date = 2015-09-03 |accessdate = 2015-09-14 |archive-date = 2015-09-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150915163918/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/riau-declares-emergency-as-haze-worsens |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/09/10/west-kalimantan-high-smog-alert.html |title= West Kalimantan on high smog alert |first= Severianus |last= Endi |work= The Jakarta Post |date= 2015-09-10 |accessdate= 2015-09-16 |archive-date= 2015-09-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150925134428/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/09/10/west-kalimantan-high-smog-alert.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2015/09/11/055699639/1500-Soldiers-Deployed-to-Fight-Forest-Fires-in-South-Kalimantan |title= 1,500 Soldiers Deployed to Fight Forest Fires in South Kalimantan |publisher= Tempo |date= 2015-09-11 |accessdate= 2015-09-16 |archive-date= 2015-09-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150915184207/http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2015/09/11/055699639/1500-Soldiers-Deployed-to-Fight-Forest-Fires-in-South-Kalimantan |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name= "worsen">{{cite news | url = http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/riau-declares-emergency-as-haze-worsens | title = Riau declares emergency as haze worsens | first1 = Wahyudi | last1 = Soeriaatmadja | first2 = Samantha | last2 = Boh | first3 = Linette | last3 = Lai | work = The Straits Times | date = 2015-09-15 | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | archive-date = 2015-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150915163918/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/riau-declares-emergency-as-haze-worsens | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/multimedia/land-fires-thick-haze-central-kalimantan-capital/ |title= Land Fires: Thick Haze in Central Kalimantan Capital |work= Jakarta Globe |accessdate= 2015-09-16 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150921201537/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/multimedia/land-fires-thick-haze-central-kalimantan-capital/ |archivedate= 2015-09-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/09/15/379-hot-spots-detected-south-kalimantan.html|title = 379 hot spots detected in South Kalimantan|work = The Jakarta Post|date = 2015-09-15|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2015-09-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150916233638/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/09/15/379-hot-spots-detected-south-kalimantan.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name = "involved">{{cite web |url= http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/100519/police-name-126-people-as-suspects-in-land-fire-cases |title= Police name 126 people as suspects in land fire cases |publisher= Antara |date= 2015-09-15 |accessdate= 2015-09-16 |archive-date= 2015-09-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150925144124/http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/100519/police-name-126-people-as-suspects-in-land-fire-cases |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

由於霾害關係，[[印尼國家治災機構|印尼國家治災機構]]（BNPB）於2015年9月4日在印尼[[廖內省|廖內]]、[[占碑省|占碑]]、[[南蘇門答臘省|南蘇門答臘]]、[[西加里曼丹省|西加里曼丹]]、[[中加里曼丹省|中加里曼丹]]和[[南加里曼丹省|南加里曼丹]]6個省份頒布[[緊急狀態令|緊急狀態令]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Oktama|first1=Carla Isati|title=Six Provinces Declare State of Emergency as Haze Worsens|url=http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/featured-2/six-provinces-declare-state-emergency-haze-worsens|work=The Jakarta Globe|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004113614/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/featured-2/six-provinces-declare-state-emergency-haze-worsens|archive-date=2015-10-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[印尼政府|印尼政府]]也於9月14日在廖內省頒布另一道緊急狀態令<ref name="worsen"/><ref name="chokes">{{cite web|url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/9/14/indonesia-declares-emergency-in-haze-hit-riau-province.html|title=Indonesia declares emergency as brush-fire smoke chokes region|publisher=Al Jazeera America|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918011018/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/9/14/indonesia-declares-emergency-in-haze-hit-riau-province.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在廖內省省會[[北干巴魯|北干巴魯]]，被迫撤離和逃到附近[[棉蘭|棉蘭]]和[[巴東|巴東]]市的居民數以千計<ref name="Wahyudi Soeriaatmadja">{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/thousands-flee-pekanbaru-as-haze-hits-record-high|title=Thousands flee Pekanbaru as haze hits record high|author=Wahyudi Soeriaatmadja|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918003339/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/thousands-flee-pekanbaru-as-haze-hits-record-high|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AsiaOne">{{cite web|url=http://news.asiaone.com/news/asia/jakarta-declares-emergency-riau-over-haze|title=Jakarta declares emergency in Riau over haze|publisher=AsiaOne|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918001933/http://news.asiaone.com/news/asia/jakarta-declares-emergency-riau-over-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印尼在[[中加里曼丹省|中加里曼丹省]]錄得的[[空氣污染指數|空氣污染指數]]水平（按照PM10濃度計算）曾在當年9月底升至2300點，又一度於10月底升至3000點，創下歷史新高<ref name=I2300>{{cite web|last1=Soeriaatmadja|first1=Wahyudi|title=Thick haze grounds firefighting copters|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/thick-haze-grounds-firefighting-copters|accessdate=2015-10-04|work=The Straits Times|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005201621/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/thick-haze-grounds-firefighting-copters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hmetro.com.my/node/87253|title=IPU Palangkaraya 3,000|date=2015-10-22|work=Harian Metro|publisher=New Straits Times Press|language=ms|accessdate=2015-10-28|location=Palangkaraya|archive-date=2015-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028030543/http://www.hmetro.com.my/node/87253|dead-url=no}}</ref>。單是印尼，受災人數就已經多於2800萬人，當中有超過14萬人報稱患[[上呼吸道|上呼吸道]]疾病<ref name=28M>{{cite web|title=Indonesia needs better aircraft for water-bombing operations|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/indonesia-needs-better-aircraft-for-water-bombing-operations|work=The Straits Times|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007213038/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/indonesia-needs-better-aircraft-for-water-bombing-operations|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=illnessnumber/>。

