== 背景 ==
印尼當局多年來一直都致力於壓制這種山火。印尼在2014年9月批准《[[东盟跨境烟霾污染协议|东盟跨境烟霾污染协议]]》，並成為最後一個批准這份協議的東盟成員國<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.menlh.go.id/indonesia-meratifikasi-undang-undang-tentang-pengesahan-asean-agreement-on-transboundary-haze-pollution-persetujuan-asean-tentang-pencemaran-asap-lintas-batas/|title=Indonesia Meratifikasi Undang-Undang Tentang Pengesahan Asean Agreement On Transboundary Haze Pollution (Persetujuan Asean Tentang Pencemaran Asap Lintas Batas)|language=id|publisher=Ministry of Environment, Indonesia|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920063146/http://www.menlh.go.id/indonesia-meratifikasi-undang-undang-tentang-pengesahan-asean-agreement-on-transboundary-haze-pollution-persetujuan-asean-tentang-pencemaran-asap-lintas-batas/|archive-date=2015-09-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。協議呼籲印尼憑着自身的努力和國際合作來實行措施，解決霧霾問題，否則印尼則需要為霧霾對東南亞鄰國的影響而面臨法律程序<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kxan.com/ap/image-of-asia-wildfire-haze-shrouds-indonesias-neighbors/|title=Image of Asia: Wildfire haze shrouds Indonesia’s neighbors|work=The Associated Press|publisher=Kxan|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925013203/http://kxan.com/ap/image-of-asia-wildfire-haze-shrouds-indonesias-neighbors/|archivedate=2015-09-25}}</ref>。新加坡也在2014年通過法律，准許新加坡當局檢控引發霧霾的個人和財團<ref name="bbcCause" />。雖然柬埔寨、[[老撾|老撾]]、泰國、[[緬甸|緬甸]]和越南已經在2015年8月初舉行會議，商討霧霾問題，不過印尼卻沒有參加這次會議<ref name="khmer hit">{{cite web|url=http://www.khmertimeskh.com/news/16585/indonesian-haze-may-be-choking-cambodia/|title=Indonesian Haze May be Choking Cambodia|author=Jonathan Cox|publisher=Khmer Times|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-08}}</ref>。

=== 成因 ===
引致霧霾的山火由從事非法[[刀耕火種|刀耕火種]]活動（俗稱燒芭），以這種廉價方式平整土地的財團和農民造成。在印尼[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]和[[加里曼丹|加里曼丹]]，佔地廣闊的[[泥炭沼澤森林|泥炭沼澤森林]]到了旱季就會變得容易着火，而由一層層植物殘體堆積物和有機物質組成的[[泥炭|泥炭]]也會因為密度的關係而產生大量碳排放物。<ref>{{cite news | title = Peatland Fires Biggest Contributor to Carbon Emissions: Researcher | newspaper = Jakarta Globe | url = http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/environment/peatland-fires-biggest-contributor-carbon-emissions-scientist/ | access-date = 2015-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151026121127/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/environment/peatland-fires-biggest-contributor-carbon-emissions-scientist/ | archive-date = 2015-10-26 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>在2015年，由於[[厄爾尼諾現象|厄爾尼諾現象]]令當地氣候更為乾旱，所以山火擴散的速度會變得更快，而山火引發的霧霾也會變得特別嚴重。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dw.com/en/why-southeast-asias-haze-problem-persists/a-18715535 |title= Why Southeast Asia's haze problem persists |first= Gabriel |last= Domínguez |work= Deutsche Welle |date= 2015-09-15 |accessdate= 2015-09-16 |archive-date= 2015-09-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150915171201/http://www.dw.com/en/why-southeast-asias-haze-problem-persists/a-18715535 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

一份在《[[環境研究快報|環境研究快報]]》（''Environmental Research Letters''）上發表的研究文章指出，蘇門答臘的山火排放物當中有59%並非來自人造林地或棕櫚種植地，而加里曼丹的山火排放物當中也有73%並非來自人造林地或棕櫚種植地<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.todayonline.com/world/getting-facts-right-indonesias-haze-problems | title = Getting the facts right on Indonesia’s haze problems | first = Erik | last = Meijaard | work = The Jakarta Globe | publisher = Today Online | date = 2015-09-14 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | archive-date = 2015-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150915183646/http://www.todayonline.com/world/getting-facts-right-indonesias-haze-problems | dead-url = no }}</ref>。環保人士表示，有由馬來西亞和新加坡投資者擁有的[[棕櫚油公司|棕櫚油公司]]因為涉嫌參與非法燒芭活動而被指控<ref name="burning">{{cite web|url=http://globalvoicesonline.org/2015/09/13/haze-returns-to-southeast-asia-as-indonesias-forest-fires-reach-critical-level/|title=Haze Returns to Southeast Asia as Indonesia's Forest Fires Reach Critical Level|author=Carolina|publisher=GlobalVoices|date=2015-09-13|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915011501/http://globalvoicesonline.org/2015/09/13/haze-returns-to-southeast-asia-as-indonesias-forest-fires-reach-critical-level/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name= "bbcCause">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34265922|title=What causes South East Asia's haze?|publisher=BBC|work=News|date=2015-09-16|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003010304/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34265922|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[印尼國家警察|印尼國家警察]]已經把126名人士列為在蘇門答臘和加里曼丹引發山火的嫌犯<ref name= "involved"/>。不過，印尼警察總長[[巴德罗丁·海迪|巴德罗丁·海迪]]卻表示這些案件會比涉及毒品和恐怖主義的案件更難應付<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/news/police-forest-fires-difficult-tackle-terrorism/|title=Police: Forest Fires More Difficult to Tackle Than Terrorism|work=Jakarta Globe|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150917231755/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/news/police-forest-fires-difficult-tackle-terrorism|archive-date=2015-09-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。廖內省原警察總長蘇集塔迪（Sutjiptadi）披露了當地人燒芭的三大動機：一、燒芭是一種便宜的土地平整方式，而且在當地作業的公司也常常捨棄其他方法，並採用這種方式。二、大部分在當地作業的公司都嘗試避免在[[林地復育|人工造林]]這方面花費。印尼所有在林地作業的持牌公司都必須運用政府發放的款項重新種植樹林，不過當中大部分公司都沒有這樣做，還會為了避免偵測而放火焚燒林地。三，這些公司會藉着砍伐和焚燒不再有生產力的老棕櫚樹來更新棕櫚種植地；雖然當地法規規定這些公司必須在混凝土基礎上完成這種焚燒作業，以免山火擴散，不過為了減低成本，大部分公司卻沒有這樣做<ref name= "motives">{{cite web|url=http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2015/09/16/055701104/Former-Riau-Police-Chief-Reveals-Three-Motives-for-Forest-Burning|title=Former Riau Police Chief Reveals Three Motives for Forest Burning|author=Arkhelaus Wisnu|publisher=Tempo|date=2015-09-16|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919111746/http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2015/09/16/055701104/Former-Riau-Police-Chief-Reveals-Three-Motives-for-Forest-Burning|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 受災各國 ==
[[File:Satellite_image_of_2015_Southeast_Asian_haze_-_20150924.jpg|upright=1.35]]在2015年9月24日拍攝，顯示霾害嚴重程度的衛星圖像]]
[[東南亞國家聯盟|東盟]]十國當中，遭受霾害的國家至少有6個，包括[[泰國|泰國]]（南部）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/haze-netizens-four-countries-share-their-gripe-73010|title=Haze: Netizens from four countries share their gripe|author1=Kohilah Sekaran|author2=Syafique Shuib|publisher=Astro Awani|date=2015-09-12|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003174658/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/haze-netizens-four-countries-share-their-gripe-73010|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thai affected">{{cite web|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/environment/679996/haze-blocks-out-hat-yai-trang|title=Haze blocks out Hat Yai, Trang|author=DPA|publisher=Bangkok Post|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-09-14}}</ref>、[[越南|越南]]（南部），以及[[汶萊|汶萊]]、印尼、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]和[[新加坡|新加坡]]（大部分地區）。[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[宿霧市|宿霧市]]和[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]][[金邊|金邊]]霧霾的起源也可能是印尼，而不是本國<ref name="khmer hit"/><ref name="PH suspects">{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/107954-philippines-suspects-haze-indonesia-fires|title=Philippines suspects week-long haze from Indonesia fires|work=Agence France-Presse|publisher=Rappler|date=2015-10-03|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018143437/http://www.rappler.com/nation/107954-philippines-suspects-haze-indonesia-fires|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[國際財經時報|國際財經時報]]》網站在2015年9月25日刊登了一幅互動前後對比圖，由此可見霧霾令新加坡和印尼的能見度大幅降低<ref name=IBTimesPhotos>{{cite web|title=Singapore and Indonesia haze: Interactive before-and-after photos show dramatically reduced visibility|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/singapore-indonesia-haze-interactive-before-after-photos-show-dramatically-reduced-visibility-1521643|accessdate=2015-10-01|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002024812/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/singapore-indonesia-haze-interactive-before-after-photos-show-dramatically-reduced-visibility-1521643|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

全球燃燒排放物数据库报道2015年印尼大火产生了约6亿吨[[温室气体|温室气体]]，並形容這“大致相当于德国全年的（溫室氣體）排放量”。[[美国太空总署|美国太空总署]]表示2015年的霾害可能成為當地有紀錄以來最嚴重的霾害危機，造成的損失也可能比造成約90亿美元損失的[[1997年东南亚霾害|1997年霾害]]多<ref>{{cite web|title=Indonesian fires sending haze across south-east Asia could become worst on record, NASA warns|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-10-02/indonesia-forest-fires-could-become-worst-on-record-nasa-warns/6824460|publisher=ABC Online|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003112548/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-10-02/indonesia-forest-fires-could-become-worst-on-record-nasa-warns/6824460|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 汶萊 ===
由於霾害發生時汶萊的主要風向是西南風，所以[[加里曼丹|加里曼丹]]的山火也為汶萊帶來霧霾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://englishnews.thaipbs.or.th/brunei-haze-may-last-for-a-week|title=Brunei haze may last for a week|work=The Brunei Times|publisher=Thai PBS|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925092804/http://englishnews.thaipbs.or.th/brunei-haze-may-last-for-a-week|archive-date=2015-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。汶萊氣象局的值班天氣預報員努魯莉娜妮·哈吉·佳哈里（Nurulinani Haji Jahari）表示由於西風仍然會令源於加里曼丹和蘇門答臘的霧霾吹向汶萊，所以當地滂沱的雷雨在消除霧霾這方面只有很小的效力。9月15日[[汶萊行政區劃|汶萊四縣]]的[[空氣污染指數|空氣污染指數]]水平當中，以[[都東縣|都東縣]]最高（68點），[[馬來奕縣|馬來奕縣]]（67點）、[[汶萊摩拉縣|汶萊摩拉縣]]（65點）和[[淡布隆縣|淡布隆縣]]（48點）次之。汶萊當局已建議汶萊公眾應該在身體健康轉差的時候多喝水和就醫，而當地公眾也已經收到警告，得悉公開燒芭等活動會令霾害的災情轉差<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.asiaone.com/news/asia/hazy-conditions-persist-brunei-week|title=Hazy conditions to persist in Brunei this week|author=Wail Wardi Wasil|work=The Brunei Times/Asia News Network|publisher=AsiaOne|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926105632/http://news.asiaone.com/news/asia/hazy-conditions-persist-brunei-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 柬埔寨 ===
[[金邊|金邊]]上空在當年10月初已被霧霾籠罩；[[柬埔寨環境部|柬埔寨環境部]]表示由印尼種植地地主引起的山火可能是柬埔寨被霧霾侵襲的成因，不過他們對此並不肯定，因為印尼已經公開，與這些刺鼻霧霾的確實來源有關的資訊很少<ref name="khmer hit"/>。

=== 印尼 ===

印尼在2015年6月底就已經受霧霾影響，有報導稱自6月28日起，霧霾便已經在蘇門答臘[[廖內省|廖內省]][[杜邁_(廖內省)|杜邁市]]出現<ref name=June15/>。在接下來的幾個月裏，這個問題仍然持續下去<ref name=IndonesiaSchools/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Nazeer|first1=Zubaidah|title=Haze blankets parts of Sumatra|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-blankets-parts-of-sumatra|work=The Straits Times|accessdate=2015-10-11|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005131326/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-blankets-parts-of-sumatra|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

截至10月7日，因為霧霾而患上呼吸道疾病的印尼人已超過14萬人<ref name=illnessnumber/>，而截至9月15日，當地大約有25,834人患上呼吸道感染疾病，有538患上[[肺炎|肺炎]]，有2,246人出現皮膚過敏的情況，還有1,656人出現眼睛過敏的情況<ref name="cihan">{{cite web|url=https://en.cihan.com.tr/en/over-30000-people-affected-by-haze-in-riau-indonesia-1893941.htm|title=Over 30,000 people affected by haze in Riau, Indonesia|publisher=Cihan|date=2015-09-18|accessdate=2015-09-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151009040231/https://en.cihan.com.tr/en/over-30000-people-affected-by-haze-in-riau-indonesia-1893941.htm|archivedate=2015-10-09}}</ref>。霧霾籠罩着[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]島全境和[[加里曼丹|加里曼丹]]部分地區，波及範圍包括旅遊業、航空業和航海業活動，以至於印尼的經濟<ref name="menguap">{{cite web|url=http://fokus.kontan.co.id/news/asap-bikin-ekonomi-ikut-menguap|title=Asap bikin ekonomi ikut menguap|language=id|author1=Hendra Gunawan|author2=Agus Triyono|author3=Noverius Laoli|publisher=Kontan.co.id|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918001149/http://fokus.kontan.co.id/news/asap-bikin-ekonomi-ikut-menguap|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/100446/more-indonesia-airports-affected-by-haze-from-land-fires|title=More Indonesia airports affected by haze from land fires|author=Juwita Trisna Rahayu|publisher=Antara|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915021607/http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/100446/more-indonesia-airports-affected-by-haze-from-land-fires|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://regional.kontan.co.id/news/bmkg-asap-kebakaran-menyelimuti-seluruh-sumatera/2015/09/04|title=BMKG: Asap kebakaran menyelimuti seluruh Sumatera|language=id|author=Havid Vebri|work=Antara|publisher=Kontan.co.id|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925091313/http://regional.kontan.co.id/news/bmkg-asap-kebakaran-menyelimuti-seluruh-sumatera/2015/09/04|archive-date=2015-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。該國霾害嚴重的省份當中，廖內省已進入緊急狀態<ref name="chokes"/>；在廖內省省會北干巴魯，當局下令學校停課，以免學生暴露在霧霾之中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/08/03/islands-focus-city-extend-school-closure-over-haze-frenzy.html|title=Islands in focus: City to extend school closure over haze frenzy|publisher=The Jakarta Post|date=2015-08-03|accessdate=2015-09-17|archive-date=2015-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911024156/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/08/03/islands-focus-city-extend-school-closure-over-haze-frenzy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.riaupos.co/85486-berita--sekolah-kembali-diliburkan,-sampai-kondisi-membaik.html|title=Sekolah Kembali Diliburkan, Sampai Kondisi Membaik|language=id|author1=Dofi Iskandar|author2=Yudi Waldi|publisher=Riau Pos|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925124124/http://www.riaupos.co/85486-berita--sekolah-kembali-diliburkan,-sampai-kondisi-membaik.html|archive-date=2015-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而當地也有數以千計的居民被迫逃離原居的城市<ref name="Wahyudi Soeriaatmadja"/><ref name="AsiaOne"/>。有報導指出，「每天」都有前往北干巴魯和[[東加里曼丹省|東加里曼丹省]][[巴厘巴板|巴厘巴板]]的航班因為視野模糊而需要取消<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.liputan6.com/read/2317321/kabut-asap-batalkan-70-penerbangan-di-bandara-ssk-ii-pekanbaru|title=Kabut asap batalkan 70 penerbangan di Bandara Sultan Syarif Kasim II|author1=M Syukur|author2=Yusron Fahmi|language=id|publisher=Liputan 6|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925113757/http://news.liputan6.com/read/2317321/kabut-asap-batalkan-70-penerbangan-di-bandara-ssk-ii-pekanbaru|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://regional.kompas.com/read/2015/09/12/20070481/Asap.Kiriman.Ganggu.Belasan.Jadwal.Penerbangan.di.Balikpapan.Setiap.Hari|title=Asap Kiriman Ganggu Belasan Jadwal Penerbangan di Balikpapan Setiap Hari|author1=Dani Julius|author2=Sandro Gatra|language=id|publisher=Kompas|date=2015-09-12|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916003027/http://regional.kompas.com/read/2015/09/12/20070481/Asap.Kiriman.Ganggu.Belasan.Jadwal.Penerbangan.di.Balikpapan.Setiap.Hari|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在由[[印度尼西亞氣象、氣候和地球物理局|印尼氣象、氣候與地球物理局]]監測的印尼空氣污染指數當中，空氣污染指數水平如果升至350點或以上，就已經達到有害水平。在2015年9月22日，有新聞報道指出[[中加里曼丹省|中加里曼丹省]][[帕朗卡拉亞|帕朗卡拉亞]]的空氣污染指數水平已經上升至1986點，而在[[西加里曼丹省|西加里曼丹省]][[坤甸|坤甸]]錄得的空氣污染指數水平也達到706點<ref>{{cite web|last1=Rahadiana|first1=Reika|title=Haze Worsens as Smog Covers Singapore, Parts of Indonesia|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-09-22/haze-worsens-as-singapore-parts-of-indonesia-covered-in-smog|publisher=Bloomberg News|accessdate=2015-09-26|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925030919/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-09-22/haze-worsens-as-singapore-parts-of-indonesia-covered-in-smog|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也有報導指出當年9月底印尼在中加里曼丹省測得的空氣污染指數升破2300點，創紀錄新高。截至10月2日，中加里曼丹省的空氣污染指數水平仍然高踞於1801點，因此而引致的視野模糊問題則令滅火直升機無法到該省某些地區投擲水彈<ref name=I2300/>。

==== 救災行動及反響 ====

印尼總統[[佐科·維多多|佐科·維多多]]已經指令政府部門吊銷所有從事燒芭活動的棕櫚油公司所擁有的作業牌照，並促請當局把涉及燒芭的人士繩之於法<ref name="burning"/>。雖然佐科曾在9月承認週而復始的霾害「並不是一個可以迅速解決的問題」，不過他也堅稱印尼打擊這個問題的措施已經是「不遺餘力」，並宣稱：「不久之後你們就會看到成績，我們會在三年內解決這個問題<ref>{{cite web|title=Indonesia 'needs time' to tackle haze - Joko Widodo|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34387979|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003015638/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34387979|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」印尼當局調遣了大約2.5萬名[[印尼國民軍|印尼國民軍]]士兵去撲滅火災<ref name="id help">{{cite web|url=http://www.3news.co.nz/world/indon-accepts-international-help-on-fires-2015100820#axzz3o6L3EQED|title=Indonesia accepts international help on fires|work=Agence-France Presse|publisher=3 News NZ|date=2015-10-08|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012082051/http://www.3news.co.nz/world/indon-accepts-international-help-on-fires-2015100820#axzz3o6L3EQED|archive-date=2015-10-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並在9月15日開始進行[[人工降雨|人工降雨]]<ref name="cloudseed"/>。當局派出了14架直升機到蘇門答臘和加里曼丹投擲水彈，以把山火撲滅，另外當局也派直升機到加里曼丹進行人工降雨<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Regional/2015/09/15/Indonesia-fights-blazes-Helicopters-water-bomb-hotspots-in-Sumatra/|title=Indonesia fights blazes|work=Agence France-Presse|publisher=The Star|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150917084541/http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Regional/2015/09/15/Indonesia-fights-blazes-Helicopters-water-bomb-hotspots-in-Sumatra/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該國大部分藥房也向公眾出售氧氣瓶<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radarpekalongan.com/97134/disaat-asap-tak-kunjung-hilang-masyarakat-harus-membeli-oksigen/|title=Disaat Asap Tak Kunjung Hilang, Masyarakat Harus Membeli Oksigen|language=id|publisher=Radar Pekalongan|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117043328/http://www.radarpekalongan.com/97134/disaat-asap-tak-kunjung-hilang-masyarakat-harus-membeli-oksigen/|archivedate=2015-11-17|df=}}</ref>。

廖內和中加里曼丹各省的居民和非政府組織都投訴印尼政府在處理山火災情方面庸碌無為，沒有向他們發放援助<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/protesters-in-kalimantan/2142782.html|title=Protesters in Kalimantan decry Indonesian inaction against forest fires, haze|author=Kane Cunico|publisher=Channel News Asia|date=2015-09-22|accessdate=2015-09-22|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924170115/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/protesters-in-kalimantan/2142782.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當地部分居民和非政府組織「人民疾苦使命聯盟」甚至向馬來西亞政府致信求援<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nasional.news.viva.co.id/news/read/670367-kecewa-dengan-ri--warga-riau-ngadu-ke-malaysia|title=Kecewa dengan RI, Warga Riau Ngadu ke Malaysia|author1=Rochimawati|author2=Ali Azumar|language=id|publisher=Viva.co.id|date=2015-09-06|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908162535/http://nasional.news.viva.co.id/news/read/670367-kecewa-dengan-ri--warga-riau-ngadu-ke-malaysia|archive-date=2015-09-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media|url=http://video.metrotvnews.com/play/2015/10/05/437786/pemuda-muhammadiyah-riau-minta-bantuan-malaysia-atasi-kabut-asap|title=Pemuda Muhammadiyah Riau Minta Bantuan Malaysia Atasi Kabut Asap|author=ARV|language=id|medium=video|time=01:28|publisher=Metro TV News|date=2015-10-05|accessdate=2015-10-06|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006071138/http://video.metrotvnews.com/play/2015/10/05/437786/pemuda-muhammadiyah-riau-minta-bantuan-malaysia-atasi-kabut-asap|dead-url=no}}</ref>。廖內省部分居民和領袖宣稱中央政府故意在霾害災情逐日轉差的情況下推出緩慢而不充足的應對措施，又解釋當局一方面拒絕外國援助，另一方面卻在獨力撲滅火災這方面顯得無能，而且只能為當地居民派發不合規格的口罩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jpnn.com/read/2015/09/21/328004/Tokoh-Riau-Tuding-Pemerintahan-Jokowi-Lakukan-Genosida-|title=Tokoh Riau Tuding Pemerintahan Jokowi Lakukan Genosida|language=id|publisher=Jawa Pos|date=2015-09-21|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930202728/http://www.jpnn.com/read/2015/09/21/328004/Tokoh-Riau-Tuding-Pemerintahan-Jokowi-Lakukan-Genosida-|archive-date=2015-09-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nasional.republika.co.id/berita/nasional/umum/15/10/06/nvrvv9335-demi-allah-kabut-asap-ini-sudah-seperti-genosida|title='Demi Allah! Kabut Asap Ini Sudah seperti Genosida'|language=id|publisher=Republika Online|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009025522/http://nasional.republika.co.id/berita/nasional/umum/15/10/06/nvrvv9335-demi-allah-kabut-asap-ini-sudah-seperti-genosida|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eramuslim.com/berita/nasional/warga-riau-rezim-ini-bunuh-63-juta-rakyat-riau-pelan-pelan.htm#.VhZZ-eyqqko|title=Warga Riau: Rezim Ini Bunuh 6,3 Juta Rakyat Riau Pelan-Pelan|language=id|publisher=Era Muslim|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007235634/http://www.eramuslim.com/berita/nasional/warga-riau-rezim-ini-bunuh-63-juta-rakyat-riau-pelan-pelan.htm#.VhZZ-eyqqko|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印尼政府承諾把[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]排放量減低兩成，卻沒有就禁絕砍伐作出任何承諾的行為也遭到環保組織非議；印尼林木砍伐活動的嚴重程度已經超越[[巴西|巴西]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greenpeace.org/international/en/news/Blogs/makingwaves/Forest-fires-indonesia-pekanbaru/blog/54046/|title=Choked in smoke – living in the thick of Indonesia’s haze|author=Zamzami|publisher=Greenpeace International|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914202947/http://www.greenpeace.org/international/en/news/Blogs/makingwaves/Forest-fires-indonesia-pekanbaru/blog/54046/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印尼環保法規無力執行的現象也被人詬病：在此前的燒芭活動當中，放火燒芭的人以印尼棕櫚油公司僱員為主，就算他們的罪行已經有真憑實據佐證，就算他們已經被捕，他們仍然能設法避免遭受重罰<ref name="menguap"/>。

雖然印尼國會議員韓旦尼·慕達賽益（Hamdhani Mukhdar Said）曾就霾害向馬來西亞和新加坡雙雙致歉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/indonesian-mp-apologises/2112520.html|title=Indonesian MP apologises to Singapore, Malaysia for haze|author=Melissa Goh|publisher=Channel News Asia|date=2015-09-08|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911032602/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/indonesian-mp-apologises/2112520.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過印尼副總統[[優素福·卡拉|優素福·卡拉]]重申，印尼在最多只持續一個月的「山火」引發霧霾這個問題上並沒有向鄰國道歉的義務，而這些鄰國也不會感激印尼的綠色環境和森林在沒有火災的時候連續多個月為他們帶來新鮮的空氣<ref>{{cite web|title=Indonesia VP Kalla reiterates that Indonesia does not need to apologise to neighbours over haze|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/kalla-reiterates-that-indonesia-does-not-need-to-apologise-to-neighbours-over-haze|work=The Straits Times|accessdate=2015-09-26|archivedate=2015-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926020730/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/kalla-reiterates-that-indonesia-does-not-need-to-apologise-to-neighbours-over-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡拉也在到紐約出席聯合國會議，發表演講時提到印尼是一個「開放」的國家，歡迎所有國家協助印尼撲滅森林和泥炭火災<ref name="jusuf">{{cite web |title=Singapore should help solve haze issue, not just talk about it: Indonesian V-P Jusuf Kalla |url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/singapore-should-help-solve-haze-issue-not-just-talk-about-it-indonesian-v-p-jusuf |work=The Straits Times |accessdate=2015-09-29 |archivedate=2015-09-29 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6buCA1n5l?url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/singapore-should-help-solve-haze-issue-not-just-talk-about-it-indonesian-v-p-jusuf |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。最終印尼國家治災機構在10月向馬來西亞、新加坡和其他國家求援，請求這些國家為印尼提供更大的[[滅火飛機|滅火飛機]]<ref name=28M/>，而[[印度尼西亞內閣列表|印尼內閣]]也終於在差不多同一個時候同意接受國際援助，應對危機。佐科總統宣告印尼已經開始「與包括新加坡在內的很多國家一起做事」，另外還有其他官員表示俄羅斯也已經表明有意為印尼提供援助<ref name="finally accepted">{{cite web|url=http://vietnamnews.vn/miscellany/276819/indonesia-accepts-international-help-to-combat-fires.html|title=Indonesia accepts international help to combat fires|publisher=Việt Nam News|work=Agence France-Presse|date=2015-10-08|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012093432/http://vietnamnews.vn/miscellany/276819/indonesia-accepts-international-help-to-combat-fires.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="id help"/>。內閣秘書帕拉莫諾·阿農解釋了早前印尼拒絕新加坡援助的原因，他說：「如果我们获得援助，印尼政府不希望新加坡从中邀功<ref>{{cite web|title=Jakarta rejected earlier offers ‘over concerns S’pore would claim credit'|url=http://www.todayonline.com/world/asia/jakarta-rejected-earlier-offers-over-concerns-spore-would-claim-credit|publisher=Today|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011025258/http://www.todayonline.com/world/asia/jakarta-rejected-earlier-offers-over-concerns-spore-would-claim-credit|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

=== 馬來西亞 ===
馬來西亞當局在全國約24處地點錄得的[[空氣污染指數|空氣污染指數]]已達到不健康水平，當中以[[砂拉越|砂拉越]]、[[雪蘭莪州|雪蘭莪州]]和[[吉打州|吉打州]][[浮羅交怡|浮羅交怡]]的霾害災情最為嚴重<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-twenty-four-areas-record-unhealthy-api-readings|title=Haze in Malaysia: Unhealthy air quality in Malacca, Selangor, Kuala Lumpur, Sarawak|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914232626/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-twenty-four-areas-record-unhealthy-api-readings|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/selangor-worst-hit-by-haze-in-malaysia|title=Selangor worst hit by haze in Malaysia; air quality unhealthy in several areas|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-12|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916174248/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/selangor-worst-hit-by-haze-in-malaysia|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ssc">{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-in-malaysia-schools-in-kuching-and-samarahan-close-as-air-quality-worsens|title=Sarawak worst-hit by haze in Malaysia as schools shut|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-17|accessdate=2015-09-17|archive-date=2015-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920012423/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/haze-in-malaysia-schools-in-kuching-and-samarahan-close-as-air-quality-worsens|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/langkawi-in-malaysia-worst-hit-by-haze-as-schools-remain-shut|title=Langkawi in Malaysia worst hit by haze as schools remain shut|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-06|archive-date=2015-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014233714/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/langkawi-in-malaysia-worst-hit-by-haze-as-schools-remain-shut|dead-url=no}}</ref>，雪蘭莪州首府[[莎阿南|莎阿南]]的空氣污染指數甚至因為霧霾的關係而升至308點的危險水平<ref name="ssc"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/haze-worsens-nationwide-api-in-shah-alam-hits-hazardous-level|title=Haze worsens nationwide, API in Shah Alam hits ‘hazardous’ level|publisher=The Malay Mail Online|date=2015-10-04|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005052754/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/haze-worsens-nationwide-api-in-shah-alam-hits-hazardous-level|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當局提醒患有哮喘病和肺病的居民在居住地空氣質素改善之前應該留在室內。由於霧霾減低能見度令航空、航海視野變得模糊，因此該國航空界和航海界已進入嚴密戒備的狀態<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/malaysia-s-aviation-maritime-sectors-on-high-alert-115091300499_1.html|title=Malaysia's aviation, maritime sectors on high alert|publisher=Business Standard|date=2015-09-13|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923171622/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/malaysia-s-aviation-maritime-sectors-on-high-alert-115091300499_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據該國教育部的聲明，如果某地空氣污染指數水平突破200點，則當地所有學校都必須關閉，不過由於霾害嚴重的關係，當局曾下令砂拉越、雪蘭莪、[[森美蘭|森美蘭]]和[[马六甲|马六甲]]等州属、[[吉隆坡|吉隆坡]][[聯邦直轄區|聯邦直轄區]]和[[布城|布城]]聯邦直轄區所有學校暫時關閉，直至9月15日為止<ref name="ssc"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/09/14/Haze-schools-to-close/|title=Haze: Schools must close once API exceeds 200|publisher=The Star|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915005234/http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/09/14/Haze-schools-to-close/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/ministry-orders-closure-of-schools-in-three-states-ft|title=Ministry orders closure of schools in three states, FT|publisher=The Malay Mail|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923195412/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/ministry-orders-closure-of-schools-in-three-states-ft|dead-url=no}}</ref>。政府又在10月4日以大馬多處地點的霧霾令當地空氣污染指數達到不健康水平為由下令全國各州（[[吉蘭丹|吉蘭丹]]、沙巴、砂拉越各州除外）學校再停課兩天<ref name="ssc"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/schools-close-for-2-days-except-in-kelantan-east-malaysia-says-minister|title=Schools close for 2 days, except in Kelantan, East Malaysia|publisher=The Malaysian Insider|date=2015-10-04|accessdate=2015-10-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005163146/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/schools-close-for-2-days-except-in-kelantan-east-malaysia-says-minister|archivedate=2015-10-05}}</ref>。[[吉隆坡馬拉松|2015年渣打吉隆坡馬拉松]]主辦方也在10月3日決定以霾害災情轉差為由取消賽事<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nst.com.my/news/2015/10/kl-marathon-cancelled-due-haze|title=Standard Chartered KL Marathon cancelled due to haze|publisher=New Straits Times Online|date=2015-10-03|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004200714/http://www.nst.com.my/news/2015/10/kl-marathon-cancelled-due-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外還有一群[[馬來西亞人|馬來西亞人]]在9月中到吉隆坡印尼大使館門前示威，抗議印尼非法的燒芭行為<ref>{{cite AV media|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-videos/malaysians-protest-against-indonesias-illegal-fires-67056|title=Malaysians protest against Indonesia's illegal fires|medium=video|time=00:35|publisher=Astro Awani|date=2015-09-18|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006021357/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-videos/malaysians-protest-against-indonesias-illegal-fires-67056|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

霾害重災區的居民都收到免費的口罩，另外很多位於[[馬來西亞半島|馬來西亞半島]]的學校都被勒令停課<ref name="cs">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/15/malaysia-closes-schools-as-indonesian-forest-fires-cloak-region-in-smoke|title=Malaysia resorts to cloud-seeding in hope of clearing smoke over region|work=Agence France-Presse|publisher=The Guardian|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916103610/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/15/malaysia-closes-schools-as-indonesian-forest-fires-cloak-region-in-smoke|dead-url=no}}</ref>。和印尼一樣，馬來西亞也已經在9月15日開始進行[[人工降雨|人工降雨]]<ref name="cloudseed">{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/malaysia-and-indonesia-begin-cloud-seeding-to-fight-haze-how-cloud-seeding-works|title=Malaysia and Indonesia begin cloud seeding to fight haze: How cloud seeding works|author=Chew Hui Min|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916103608/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/malaysia-and-indonesia-begin-cloud-seeding-to-fight-haze-how-cloud-seeding-works|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在馬來西亞進行的人工降雨行動為時10天（至9月25日為止），行動範圍包括位於沙巴、砂拉越的[[古晉|古晉]]、[[詩里阿曼|詩里阿曼]]、[[三馬拉漢|三馬拉漢]]和[[泗里街|泗里街]]，以及位於馬來西亞半島的[[巴生谷|巴生谷]]地區<ref name="cs"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theborneopost.com/2015/09/15/cloud-seeding-operations-begin-today/|title=Cloud seeding operations begin today *updated*|author=Geryl Ogilvy Ruekeith|publisher=The Borneo Post|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925125123/http://www.theborneopost.com/2015/09/15/cloud-seeding-operations-begin-today/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/09/15/malaysia-to-begin-cloud-seeding-as-schools-shut-due-to-haze|title=Haze forces school closures in Malaysia, with officials to try cloud-seeding to induce rain|work=Associated Press|publisher=US News|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305170219/http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/09/15/malaysia-to-begin-cloud-seeding-as-schools-shut-due-to-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

馬來西亞首相[[納吉·阿都拉薩|納吉·阿都拉薩]]已要求印尼對付應為非法焚燒森林，令東南亞一部分地區被霧霾籠罩而負責的公司，並表示「只有印尼自己能夠收集證據並把有關公司定罪。」[[馬來西亞教育部|該國教育部長]][[馬哈茲爾卡立|馬哈茲爾卡立]]也在同時表示「我們絕對不會對任何可能會傷害學校學童的事情妥協。」<ref name="demands">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34438189|title=Malaysia's Najib Razak demands Indonesia take action over haze|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-10-05|accessdate=2015-10-06|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007205048/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34438189|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[馬來西亞政府|馬來西亞政府]]還呼籲印尼批准剛剛與馬來西亞簽訂、旨在打擊跨境霧霾的[[諒解備忘錄|諒解備忘錄]]。馬來西亞[[馬來西亞天然资源与环境部|天然资源与环境部長]][[旺朱乃迪|旺朱乃迪]]說，這份諒解備忘錄會令馬、印兩國有機會「在叢林火災或者泥炭火災發生的時候相互協助和交換意見，不過與此同時印尼要遵守協議的規定」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/malaysia-indonesia-sign-new-mou-tackle-transboundary-haze-73066|title=Malaysia, Indonesia to sign new MoU to tackle transboundary haze|work=Bernama|publisher=Astro Awani|date=2015-09-12|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916220446/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/malaysia-indonesia-sign-new-mou-tackle-transboundary-haze-73066|dead-url=no}}</ref>。砂拉越[[馬來西亞消防與拯救局|消防與拯救局]]已經準備好，將在接獲相關的指示後協助撲滅坤甸的泥炭火災<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1555843|title=Sarawak Fire and Rescue Department ready to put out fires in Kalimantan|work=Bernama|publisher=The Sun|date=2015-09-17|accessdate=2015-09-19|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926020415/http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1555843|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而該國[[馬來西亞國防部|國防部長]][[希山慕丁|希山慕丁]]也提到，[[馬來西亞武裝部隊|馬來西亞軍隊]]已經向印尼提議協助印尼撲救蘇門答臘和加里曼丹的山火<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2015/09/30/055705111/Malaysia-Offers-Military-Assistance-Fighting-Forest-Fire-Haze|title=Malaysia Offers Military Assistance Fighting Forest Fire, Haze|author=Putri Adityowati|work=The Malay Mail, Antara|publisher=Tempo|date=2015-09-30|accessdate=2015-09-30|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001162332/http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2015/09/30/055705111/Malaysia-Offers-Military-Assistance-Fighting-Forest-Fire-Haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 菲律賓 ===
由於吹向東北方的季候風把印尼山火的排放物吹向菲律賓中部地區，因此菲律賓[[宿霧|宿霧]]島也遭受到霾害；截至2015年10月3日，當地霾害災情已持續一週<ref name="PH suspects"/>。因此，由於視野模糊的關係，當地部分飛機在[[麥克坦-宿霧國際機場|麥克坦-宿霧國際機場]]降落的時候會遇到困難。該國的[[目視飛行規則|目視飛行規則]]已經停止實行，航空公司必須擁有具備[[儀器飛行|儀器飛行]]能力的航機，才可以駕駛航機在當地的機場起飛和降落。不具備[[儀器飛行|儀器飛行]]能力的小型飛機不得在當地機場起飛和降落<ref name="PH hit">{{cite web|url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/cebu/local-news/2015/10/02/haze-hits-cebu-433513|title=‘Haze’ hits Cebu|author1=Justin K. Vestil|author2=Elias O. Baquero|publisher=Rappler|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002175017/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/cebu/local-news/2015/10/02/haze-hits-cebu-433513|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一開始的時候菲律賓並不相信印尼的霧霾已經吹到菲律賓<ref name="PH hit"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/haze-blanketing-cebu-link-to-indonesia-wildfires-dismissed/|title=Haze blanketing Cebu; link to Indonesia wildfires dismissed|author=Mars W. Mosqueda Jr.|publisher=Manila Bulletin|date=2015-10-02|accessdate=2015-10-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005031613/http://www.mb.com.ph/haze-blanketing-cebu-link-to-indonesia-wildfires-dismissed/|archivedate=2015-10-05}}</ref>，不過後來菲律賓開始懷疑霧霾源於印尼，因為一般而言影響[[宿霧市|宿霧市]]的霧霾會在一天內消散，不過這次並非如此<ref name="PH suspects"/>。

=== 新加坡 ===
霧霾吹襲新加坡後，當地大部分戶外活動都要延期舉行<ref>{{Cite web|title = Guide to the #haze in infographics|url = http://graphics.straitstimes.com/STI/STIMEDIA/Interactives/2015/09/haze-in-singapore/index.html|accessdate = 2015-09-21|archive-date = 2015-09-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920011633/http://graphics.straitstimes.com/STI/STIMEDIA/Interactives/2015/09/haze-in-singapore/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/environment/hazy-conditions-over-singapore-expected-to-continue-on-sunday-and-monday|title=Outdoor activities affected by haze on Sunday; showers expected on Monday may bring only temporary respite|author1=Calvin Yang|author2=Lee Min Kok|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-13|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915174736/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/environment/hazy-conditions-over-singapore-expected-to-continue-on-sunday-and-monday|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2015年新加坡大獎賽|2015年新加坡大獎賽]]受到霾害波及的可能在賽事舉行前一週變成一個問題<ref>{{cite web|title=Haze in Singapore back at unhealthy levels on Saturday|url=http://news.asiaone.com/news/singapore/haze-singapore-back-unhealthy-levels-saturday|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926104116/http://news.asiaone.com/news/singapore/haze-singapore-back-unhealthy-levels-saturday|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11863885/Singapore-Grand-Prix-could-be-affected-by-dangerous-smog-levels.html|title=Singapore Grand Prix could be affected by dangerous smog levels|author=Daniel Johnson|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915190724/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11863885/Singapore-Grand-Prix-could-be-affected-by-dangerous-smog-levels.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此外[[2015年国际泳联游泳世界杯|国际泳联游泳世界杯]]部分在2015年10月3日舉行的赛事也因為空气污染指数处于不健康水平而被取消<ref>{{cite web|title=FINA Swimming World Cup finals cancelled due to haze|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/fina-swimming-world-cup/2167788.html|publisher=Channel News Asia|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005225834/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/fina-swimming-world-cup/2167788.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霧霾令新加坡當局監測的空氣污染指數水平在9月14日晚上8時達到223點，突破非常不健康水平<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/NEAsg/status/643395705348853760|title=Daily PSI readings of Singapore|work=National Environment Agency (Singapore)|publisher=Twitter|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305152916/https://twitter.com/NEAsg/status/643395705348853760|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於一小時後再上升至249點，不過在隨後的晚間時段，空氣污染指數水平就開始回落到不健康水平。9月15日至16日期間的雷暴和大雨，以及同月20日至22日期間的主要風向轉變都令新加坡的霾害災情得以改善。

9月23日晚上至24日早上期間，新加坡的主要風向南風把源於蘇門答臘的濃霧吹到新加坡，令新加坡的霾害災情再度轉差<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/environment/haze-conditions-may-worsen-on-thursday-24-hour-psi-may-cross-into-very|title=Haze worsens on Thursday, 24-hour PSI edges into very unhealthy range|author=Lee Min Kok|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2015-09-24|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925090409/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/environment/haze-conditions-may-worsen-on-thursday-24-hour-psi-may-cross-into-very|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新加坡當局監測的空氣污染指數水平在9月24日晚上7時上升至313點，這是空氣污染指數在2015年內錄得有害水平的首例。一個小時之後，空氣污染水平又上升到317點。因此，該國[[新加坡教育部|教育部]]便以霾害災情轉差為由宣布當地所有中、小學要在25日停課<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/schools-to-close-on/2147982.html|publisher=Channel News Asia|accessdate=2015-09-24|author=Chan Luo Er, Leong Wai Kit|title=Schools to close on Friday due to worsening haze situation: MOE|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925134219/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/schools-to-close-on/2147982.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而[[新加坡人力部|人力部]]卻澄清同日一則在社交媒体（[[WhatsApp|WhatsApp]]或[[Facebook|Facebook]]）上發布，声称人力部因為霾害而宣布翌日為[[2015年自愿不工作日|自愿不工作日]]的帖子只是[[新加坡恶作剧列表|恶作剧]]，並已就此向警方報案<ref>{{cite web|title=MOM lodges police report over hoax post|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/mom-lodges-police-report-over-hoax-post|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929185240/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/mom-lodges-police-report-over-hoax-post|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霾害災情在接着幾個小時之內繼續轉差，而空氣污染指數水平也在25日凌晨5時升至341點，達到全年最高點。然而，3小時空氣污染指數在當日下午1時便回落到中等水平。當日下午至晚上期間，空氣污染指數水平一直在不健康水平徘徊，而教育部也宣布當地學校會在28日復課。自當日起直至10月5日，空氣污染指數一直維持在不健康水平，有時甚至上升至非常不健康水平<ref name=hazegovsg>{{cite web|title=NEA haze readings for past 24 hours (refreshed daily)|url=http://www.nea.gov.sg/anti-pollution-radiation-protection/air-pollution-control/psi/psi-readings-over-the-last-24-hours|publisher=National Environment Agency, Singapore|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150925122632/http://www.nea.gov.sg/anti-pollution-radiation-protection/air-pollution-control/psi/psi-readings-over-the-last-24-hours|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

新加坡已啟動法律程序，並有可能憑此向引發農田和種植地火災，向新加坡這個城市國家排放空氣污染物，令當地空氣質素降至不健康水平的印尼公司徵收巨额罚款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.manilatimes.net/singapore-moves-vs-indon-firms-over-haze/220785/|title=Singapore moves vs Indon firms over haze|publisher=The Manila Times|date=2015-09-26|accessdate=2015-09-27|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006135429/http://www.manilatimes.net/singapore-moves-vs-indon-firms-over-haze/220785/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而新加坡規模最大的[[新加坡职工总会平价合作社|职总平价合作社]]也已經把由涉嫌引發霧霾的印尼亞洲漿紙（Asia Pulp & Paper；APP）公司生產的紙產品下架<ref name="finally accepted"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-10-07/singapore-s-biggest-grocer-pulls-toilet-paper-in-haze-rebuke|title=Singapore Retailer Pulls Indonesian Toilet Rolls in Haze Row|author=Sharon Chen|publisher=Bloomberg|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010163041/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-10-07/singapore-s-biggest-grocer-pulls-toilet-paper-in-haze-rebuke|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新加坡當局還把庫存的補給品派發給當地居民（當中以難以防禦霧霾的老年家庭為主），例如向29000名年长居民派發的AIR+智能口罩和包含[[眼药水|眼药水]]、[[维生素C|维生素C]]片、饼干、快熟面和罐头食品等食品和日用品的爱心包（We Care PAcks）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/haze-supplies-30-000/2130702.html|title=Haze supplies: 30,000 households to get WeCare PAcks, 29,000 masks for needy elderly|author1=Xabryna Kek|author2=Hetty Musfirah Abdul Khamid|publisher=Channel News Asia|date=2015-09-16|accessdate=2015-09-17|archive-date=2015-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150917193726/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/haze-supplies-30-000/2130702.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[新加坡政府|新加坡政府]]曾先後在6月初旱季和霾害未開始的時候和9月霧霾蔓延到新加坡的時候提議為印尼提供對付霧霾的援助配套，包括三部[[C-130運輸機|C-130運輸機]]、一部[[CH-47直升機|CH-47直升機]]和一隊[[新加坡民防部隊|民防部隊]]拯救隊。<ref>{{cite web|title=Singapore renews haze assistance package offer to Indonesia|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/singapore-renews-haze/1889412.html|publisher=[[Channel_News_Asia|Channel News Asia]]|accessdate=2015-10-11|date=2015-06-03|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018140518/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/singapore-renews-haze/1889412.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theborneopost.com/2015/09/11/singapore-offers-assistance-to-indonesia-to-combat-haze/|title=Singapore offers assistance to Indonesia to combat haze|work=Bernama|publisher=The Borneo Post|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925213736/http://www.theborneopost.com/2015/09/11/singapore-offers-assistance-to-indonesia-to-combat-haze/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印尼最初表態接受援助<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/environment/indonesia-has-accepted-singapores-offer-to-help-fight-forest-fires-in-sumatra|title=Indonesia has accepted Singapore's offer to help fight forest fires in Sumatra|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914230843/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/environment/indonesia-has-accepted-singapores-offer-to-help-fight-forest-fires-in-sumatra|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過印尼環境與林業部長西蒂·努爾巴雅（Siti Nurbaya Bakar）後來卻以印尼有足夠人力物力應付這場危機為由，拒絕新加坡向印尼提供援助的提議，而這個說法也獲得環境與林業部首席發言人的確認<ref name="reject">{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/jakarta-declines-help-to-fight-fires|title=Jakarta declines help to fight fires|author=Wahyudi Soeriaatmadja|publisher=The Straits Times|date=2015-09-13|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915005533/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/jakarta-declines-help-to-fight-fires|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，印尼副總統卡拉在聯合國演講期間卻呼籲有意協助印尼救災的新加坡：「如果你們想幫忙的話，請過來，不要只是說話<ref name="jusuf"/>。」時任[[新加坡環境及水源部|新加坡環境及水源部長]][[維文_(新加坡)|維文]]在印尼拒絕新加坡援助後仍然表示新加坡有意援助印尼<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/singapore-reiterates/2125790.html|title=Singapore reiterates offer of assistance to Indonesia to fight forest fires|publisher=Channel News Asia|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916074810/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/singapore-reiterates/2125790.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在前往美國紐約，參加聯合國可持续发展峰会期間代表新加坡發佈國家聲明，呼籲東南亞區內各國和國際社會緊密合作，應對東南亞霾害問題<ref>{{cite web|title=SINGAPORE’S NATIONAL STATEMENT BY MINISTER VIVIAN BALAKRISHNAN AT THE UNITED NATIONS SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT SUMMIT 2015|url=http://www.news.gov.sg/public/sgpc/en/media_releases/agencies/mewr/press_release/P-20150928-1.html|accessdate=2015-10-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151006110235/http://www.news.gov.sg/public/sgpc/en/media_releases/agencies/mewr/press_release/P-20150928-1.html|archivedate=2015-10-06}}</ref>。到了10月7日，印尼才決定接受新加坡援助<ref>{{cite web|title=Indonesia accepts Singapore's offer of haze assistance package|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/indonesia-accepts/2175204.html|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009065841/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/indonesia-accepts/2175204.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 泰國 ===
[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]的霧霾令泰國南部大部分地區（包括[[陶公府|陶公]]、[[北大年府|北大年]]、[[布吉府|布吉]]、[[沙敦府|沙敦]]、[[宋卡府|宋卡]]、[[素叻府|素叻]]、[[董里府|董里]]和[[也拉府|也拉]]各府）的視野變得模糊不清<ref name="thai affected"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thephuketnews.com/sumatra-forest-fire-haze-returns-to-blanket-phuket-53945.php|title=Sumatra forest fire haze returns to blanket Phuket|author=Saroj Kueprasertkij|publisher=The Phuket News|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914130948/http://www.thephuketnews.com/sumatra-forest-fire-haze-returns-to-blanket-phuket-53945.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rg co-operate">{{cite web|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/asean/720720/pm-calls-for-regional-haze-cooperation|title=PM calls for regional haze cooperation|publisher=Bangkok Post|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07}}</ref>。布吉府衛生局（PPHO）就此已在2015年8月向當地居民發出健康警告<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thephuketnews.com/phuket-health-advisory-issued-over-forest-fire-haze-53838.php|title=Phuket health advisory issued over forest fire haze|author1=Saroj Kueprasertkij|author2=Tanyaluk Sakoot|publisher=The Phuket News|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911011013/http://www.thephuketnews.com/phuket-health-advisory-issued-over-forest-fire-haze-53838.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，到了10月，霧霾也令[[布吉機場|布吉機場]]出現多次航班延誤<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/Haze-causes-delays-flights-Phuket-Airport|title=Haze causes more delays for flights at Phuket Airport|author=Kritsada Mueanhawong|publisher=Phuket Gazette|date=2015-10-08|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929162923/https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/Haze-causes-delays-flights-Phuket-Airport|dead-url=no}}</ref>。泰南各府空气污染指数不断攀升，地区环境办公室第十六处主任哈勒姆·哲马里甘表示目前的空气污染水平是盛行风向和低压区令雾霾無法被吹走的結果。尽管泰南的雾霾现状不至于影响航空业，不過在很多医院，因為患上呼吸系统有关疾病而就诊儿童患者人數已大幅上升<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eco-business.com/news/thailand-southern-haze-hits-this-years-worst/|title=Thailand: Southern haze hits this year's worst|work=National News Bureau of Thailand|publisher=Eco Business|date=2015-10-05|accessdate=2015-10-06|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006084519/http://www.eco-business.com/news/thailand-southern-haze-hits-this-years-worst/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。哈勒姆又补充，比起以前會在四个小时内消散的烟雾，這次霾害是几十年来最严重的<ref name="war room">{{cite web|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/national/Haze-in-South-rises-beyond-safety-mark-30270267.html|title=Haze in South rises beyond safety mark|publisher=The Nation|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-06|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006142921/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/national/Haze-in-South-rises-beyond-safety-mark-30270267.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

泰國首相[[巴育·占奧差|巴育·占奧差]]既命令[[泰國外交部|外交部]]與鄰國緊密合作，解決這個籠罩着東南亞部分地區的長期問題<ref name="rg co-operate"/>，也指令受災[[泰國行政區劃|各府]]的官員一邊進行空中灑水，令視野更清晰，一邊向公眾派發口罩<ref name="rg co-operate"/>。泰國表示他們會在東盟的層面推動霾害問題的解決<ref name="nm"/>。泰國外交部副常務次長威塔哇（Vitavas Srivihok）表示泰國已經向印尼提議協助解決霾害，而印尼使節也已經承認印尼自身努力並不足以撲滅山火<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/general/723728/government-offers-to-help-jakarta-fight-haze-hazard|title=Government offers to help Jakarta fight haze hazard|author1=Prangthong Jitcharoenkul|author2=Patsara Jikkham|author3=Amornrat Mahitthirook|publisher=Bangkok Post|date=2015-10-09|accessdate=2015-10-10}}</ref>。[[泰國政府|泰國政府]]還推出了一個名為Air4ASEAN的應用程式，這個程式會追蹤由印尼山火引發的霧霾擴散的路徑，也會監測各個受災國家的空氣質素<ref name="khmer hit"/>。在地方層面，宋卡府尹松波·萨瓦迪譚已經設立了一個“作战室”，為受灾居民提供援助，以对抗印尼森林大火产生的烟雾所帶來的影响<ref name="war room"/>。當地大約有50個[[泰國人|泰國人]]在印尼駐宋卡領事館門前舉行了一場示威，要求印尼政府加快滅火行動<ref name="nm">{{cite web|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/national/PM-Asean-help-needed-on-smog-30270326.html|title=PM: Asean help needed on smog|publisher=The Nation|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008232126/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/national/PM-Asean-help-needed-on-smog-30270326.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外還有20個代表「受印尼霧霾影響的合艾－宋卡居民」組織的泰國人致函印尼領事館，要求印尼為霾害負責，並承諾會解決霾害問題<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1574046|title=Thais send letter of complaint to Indonesia|work=Bernama|publisher=The Sun|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021001625/http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1574046|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 越南 ===
自10月4日起，[[胡志明市|胡志明市]]和越南南部其他省份都被霧霾侵襲。專家相信印尼的山火是這個現象出現的其中一個原因。越南國家水文氣象中心南部區域水文氣象台表示，自10月初開始，[[湄公河三角洲|湄公河三角洲]]地區[[朔莊省|朔莊]]、[[金甌省|金甌]]、[[堅江省|堅江]]、[[同塔省|同塔]]、[[檳椥省|檳椥]]和[[芹苴市|芹苴]]等省市也出現了類似的多霧天氣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tuoitrenews.vn/society/30851/indonesia-forest-fires-to-blame-for-foggy-ho-chi-minh-city-expert|title=Southern Vietnam enters third day of choking haze apparently from Indonesia fires (photos)|publisher=Tuoi Tre News|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008153531/http://tuoitrenews.vn/society/30851/indonesia-forest-fires-to-blame-for-foggy-ho-chi-minh-city-expert|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於越南南部出現皮膚過敏、流鼻血、鼻敏感、打噴嚏症狀的兒童病人人數有所增加，當地居民已接到留在室內的提醒。南部區域水文氣象台在10月9日估計當地接下來三天會繼續出現霧霾現象，此後大雨便會逐漸令霧霾消散<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.vietnamnet.vn/fms/society/143553/dry-haze-sends-rising-number-of-southern-children-to-hospitals.html|title=Dry haze sends rising number of southern children to hospitals|publisher=Vietnam Net|date=2015-10-09|accessdate=2015-10-09|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010154621/http://english.vietnamnet.vn/fms/society/143553/dry-haze-sends-rising-number-of-southern-children-to-hospitals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

